{
  "stem": "1062.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And, you know, IG farm went to the SS, and they-- and they hired us as labor.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And apparently the SS got paid for us, to feed us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "Now, we were staying in Buna.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "In the morning, in Buna, you got up and first of all, we had barracks, you know And the barracks were bunks.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "They were three in a row, you know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And they had-- they had like barrels in the middle.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "First of all, when I was in Birkenau, they used to have like-- in the barrack, there was long stoves-- long stoves.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "About maybe 60, 70 feet long-- that was for heating purposes.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "Because at one time, that used to be for horses.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "On either side of the stove was a chimney.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "When you go back to Auschwitz, you don't see the chimney and those long stoves.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "But they used to use those stoves, what they used to do is they used to take somebody and put them in there, and then beat them.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "So the stove, I mean this long thing, would muffle the sound out.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "But in Buna, we had barracks, regular barracks, because this was, you know-- IG farm had a factory, the Buna factory, where they made synthetic rubber.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "And in case you had to go at night to the bathroom, so you went to the barrel-- there were barrels lined up.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "And when the barrel was full, [LAUGHS] whoever was lucky enough, you know, then you had to take the barrel out, someplace out-- carry it.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "It was heavy.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So some people did not go to the barrel, so-- [LAUGHS] so they peed them on top of the other.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So the guy who was in the bottom, he got the worse part of it.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
